<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>New Reply on Your Support Ticket</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F46E5 0%, #7C3AED 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .ticket-number {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #4F46E5;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #4338CA;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .message-box {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .message-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .message-author {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .message-time {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .message-body {
      color: #374151;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      background: #dbeafe;
      color: #1e40af;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>ðŸ’¬ New Reply Received</h1>
    <div class="ticket-number">#{{ticketNumber}}</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
    
    <p>Great news! Our support team has responded to your ticket.</p>
    
    <div class="message-box">
      <div class="message-header">
        <div>
          <span class="message-author">{{senderName}}</span>
          <span class="badge">Support Team</span>
        </div>
        <span class="message-time">{{timestamp}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="message-body">{{message}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{ticketUrl}}" class="button">View Full Conversation</a>
    </div>
    
    <p><strong>Need to follow up?</strong> You can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Reply directly to this email</li>
      <li>Add a comment via the ticket portal</li>
      <li>Call us if you need immediate assistance</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>We're here to help! If this resolves your issue, you can close the ticket from your dashboard.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p><strong>Ticket:</strong> #{{ticketNumber}} - {{subject}}</p>
    <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
    <p>To unsubscribe from ticket notifications, update your preferences in your account settings.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
